Package com.vmware.esx.settings.hardware_support

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Managers
    The Managers interface provides methods to list Hardware Support Manager (HSM) for a given vCenter.
    ManagersTypes
    Defines the data types of the Managers API service.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    HardwareSupportFactory
    HardwareSupportFactory is responsible for creating instances of services contained inside the com.vmware.esx.settings.hardware_support package and also has the subpackages reference to access respective subpackage services.
    ManagersDefinitions
    Defines the type descriptors for the Managers API service.
    ManagersStub
    Remote stub implementation of the Managers API service.
    ManagersTypes.HardwareSupportManagerInfo
    The HardwareSupportManagerInfo class contains properties that describe a particular 3rd party Hardware Support Manager (HSM)
    ManagersTypes.HardwareSupportManagerInfo.Builder
    Builder class for ManagersTypes.HardwareSupportManagerInfo.
    StructDefinitions
    Defines the type descriptors for the top-level types in com.vmware.esx.settings.hardware_support package.
